                  </hi>.</p>
               <p>(<hi rend="italic">Simpson was further charged with having been before convicted</hi>.)</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18551126-name-550" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18551126-name-550" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
