                        <interp inst="t18551126-name-550" type="given" value="GEORGE"></interp>GEORGE QUINNEAR</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-sergeant, P</hi> 1). I produce a certificate (<hi rend="italic">Read: "St. Mary, Newington, <persName id="t18551126-name-551">
                        <interp inst="t18551126-name-551" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18551126-name-551" type="surname" value="WILLIAMS"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18551126-name-551" type="given" value="PETER"></interp>Peter Williams</persName>, Convicted, May</hi>, 1852, <hi rend="italic">of stealing</hi> 30 <hi rend="italic">lbs. weight of veal; having then been before convicted: 
Transported for ten years</hi>")—Simpson is the man—I was present at his trial.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
GUILTY</hi>.—<hi rend="italic">
